                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Planteur mal élevé, sache que les vestales",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "À qui la lune, en son équivoque œil-de-chat,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Est la rosace de l'unique cathédrale,",
